{"tid":2478274,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"TVB大股東黎瑞剛狠批TVB節目老化 急須改革 建議用內地創富故事啟發港人","createTime":"2021-04-07T02:33:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T03:04:12.000Z","uid":130626,"like":5,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"89b94572434300504ad34aca90698288ef329d5e","tid":2478274,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T02:33:16.000Z","msg":"電視廣播（TVB，511）大股東黎瑞剛接受傳媒專訪時指，對TVB「非常不滿意」，批評TVB節目老化、製作技術落後、內部山頭林立等五大缺失，直言電視台離年輕觀眾越來越遠，需要引入更多創意節目，包括內地青年的創富故事，以啟發香港年輕觀眾，同時他表示日後將積極參與TVB的運作。<br />\n<br />\n黎瑞剛接受《星島日報》專訪，他形容TVB已「迷失十年」，並對大台「不滿意，不滿意，而且是非常不滿意」。他狠斥TVB創新乏力，由管理團隊以至節目均全面老化，而且「山頭林立，矛盾很多，難以形成合力」，管理層決策亦失誤，例如買入星美控股債券以及其他債券，導致公司蒙受重大損失，撇帳高達8.3億元，即使開拓電商業務Big Big Shop，使用體驗也很差。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210407/SXQ6B57NAFDZZDI2SMZJAPGE3U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210407%2FSXQ6B57NAFDZZDI2SMZJAPGE3U%2F&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtGipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=a1c944e3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210407%2FSXQ6B57NAFDZZDI2SMZJAPGE3U%2F&h=65a33ed9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210407/SXQ6B57NAFDZZDI2SMZJAPGE3U/</a>"},{"pid":"58a2d2c2be46e944b43b790a75d7a4474ad05dc0","tid":2478274,"uid":16676,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T02:36:28.000Z","msg":"係咪自揭<br />\n<br />\n市場封閉<br />\n貪污賄賂<br />\n走後門<br />\n<br />\n原來有人真係天真以為支那所謂致富係正財行正路<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"849ab69c331de6e350abdd8a0d68e05197c572b7","tid":2478274,"uid":224375,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T02:37:43.000Z","msg":"之前班友先吹到BIG BIG SHOP 有幾多百萬會員，比原先既訂目標早左一年就達成 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n面對現實啦ON鳩，而家邊個PRODUCT 同BIG BIG SHOP合作，網民就會封殺個PRODUCT，搵鬼JOIN 咩 <br />\n<br />\n屌你老味真係貽笑大方 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9001dea97c27261db05f647c918e5c92f4c90ed9","tid":2478274,"uid":53498,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T02:41:05.000Z","msg":"嫌未夠党化,要再支那洗腦味重啲"},{"pid":"b743f5d556f3ecf0b815c5e634ac7962ed849631","tid":2478274,"uid":93479,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T02:41:21.000Z","msg":"不如將內地一系列上過胡潤百富榜龍頭的巨富<br />\n<br />\n點樣發跡到點樣下馬下獄<br />\n一定好好睇"},{"pid":"0cbd1f600eb6beb4b7458f9ea2671ea4a4503308","tid":2478274,"uid":21896,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T02:41:26.000Z","msg":"成日都話要改革創新，其實香港好多公司包括tvb，以為整個app/改下呢樣改下個樣就叫創新，但成間公司個思維仲係以前個套<br />\n我而家做緊呢間香港公司就係咁，好撚多新project，但呢啲project純粹係因為公司開完個annual conference得出要創新就一窩蜂搞出嚟，班高層就為左交功課，我地做落就覺得都係用舊個套帶動新idea,結果就係你更加依賴舊個套因為你連新個套都係base on原本樣野黎做"},{"pid":"abf4ff78788283a42d26d14525bf60e304bf9fc4","tid":2478274,"uid":120499,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T02:42:47.000Z","msg":"需要引入更多創意節目，包括內地青年的創富故事，以啟發香港年輕觀眾<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2ac1735c0b21d13ecbcd8bf8d6a67e5648310d6","tid":2478274,"uid":147367,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTi